screen_desc: A pop-up notification on a mobile device screen is asking for location access permission for the Uber app. The options provided are "WHILE USING THE APP," "ONLY THIS TIME," and "DON'T ALLOW." The time displayed on the device is 10:54 AM, and the battery is fully charged at 100%.

ui_elements.text: Allow Uber to access this device’s location?
ui_elements.content_desc: "Permission message asking to allow Uber to access the device’s location"
